{"tid":2511121,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"廣東歌係咪已經開始踏入另一個新世紀?","createTime":"2021-04-30T15:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T07:23:57.000Z","uid":391618,"like":104,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"e1753df44706a1d41c31410c46d1badbd1666e3c","tid":2511121,"uid":391618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:59:23.000Z","msg":"10年前差唔多全部都係canton-pop style情情愛愛失戀歌<br />\n2019年之後唔知係咪香港人覺醒咗定係精神層面昇華咗<br />\n香港人唔再日日loop失戀歌, 各式各樣題材同style廣東歌創作開始大爆發<br />\n下面舉幾個例子, 10年前根本唔會有人作呢類歌, 甚至諗到呢類cls題材, 就算有都未必會賣坐<br />\n<span class=\"violet\">比較熱門大路:</span><br />\n<ins><strong>狂人日記 - 一個痴線佬嘅三生三世輪迴故事</strong></ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Fo0kczTrfeE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFo0kczTrfeE&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRAjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=bf2e4655\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Fo0kczTrfeE</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>一人之境 - 描繪自閉症嘅內心世界</strong></ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qWhavDVsMRc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqWhavDVsMRc&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRAjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=5a1ece49\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qWhavDVsMRc</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>多喝水 - 見字飲水都可以作到首歌, 勁!</ins></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NR6RZVgQgb0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNR6RZVgQgb0&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRAjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=8b38f830\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NR6RZVgQgb0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"violet\">比較冷門少少:</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>我想行開下 - 我想行開下我想行開下我想行開下我想行開下我想行開下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BRdq784er3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBRdq784er3s&