img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0629ffe1b466a2cc90a1e1771776b464cd66f4ca","tid":2511121,"uid":391618,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b6f470a099180442cf33ca943929dfd495508dac","tid":2511121,"uid":57674,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T16:14:38.000Z","msg":"AK首黑之呼吸呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T16:17:48.000Z","msg":"我們總是覺得黑色感覺負面，卻忘了其實黑色是所有色光被吸收所造成，就以顏料為例，把不同的顏色混在一起，最後就變成黑色。<br />\n如果三原色各自代表一些人的感受與特性，<span class=\"red\">紅色代表衝動、愛</span>；<span class=\"gold\">黃色代表單純、童心</span>；<span class=\"blue\">藍色代表悲傷、冷靜</span>⋯⋯那麼黑色，比起其他顏色更加像一個人。因為人就是由大量情緒面向混集而成。<br />\n有情緒從來沒有錯，向大眾真誠地展露這種黑，或許會招惹口舌，引來謠言；但既然黑是百種色，混於這世間，或者保持這種真才能令自己活得像自己。<br />\n旅程繼續，保持呼吸，願黑中有光。"},{"pid":"4f0b02cab3664259b4887d0c1a7cf5cd500880b2","tid":2511121,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T16:55:50.000Z","msg":"支持本地樂壇"},{"pid":"382f77a41bb19d8d5f12d5c12a8e13e4b7825ab9","tid":2511121,"uid":160589,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"838e566020eafa4f7fef1d1faa4f5e080986a1ae","tid":2511121,"uid":238920,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T16:04:16.000Z","msg":"其實好多年前己經唔係得情情愛愛架啦<br />\n淫Kay未生女前已經有一大堆講社會同人既歌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T16:57:24.000Z","msg":"Juno講佛理"},{"pid":"e4223c26c966346a9cb8d0bcea3cfcff57288d15","tid":2511121,"uid":160589,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e8de3dee4da95b20369712dd3eb446a11e9ae95","tid":2511121,"uid":24457,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T16:11:13.000Z","msg":"情情愛愛嘅歌一早過咗好耐 之前多到阿媽都唔認得嘅係勵志歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T16:58:16.000Z"